org.krmdemo.techlabs.core.dump.StringBuilderOut
All Implemented Interfaces:
Closeable, Flushable, Appendable, AutoCloseable, CharSequence
public class StringBuilderOut extends PrintStream implements CharSequence
A PrintWriter over StringBuilderWriter that could simplify the substitution of System.out and System.err in unit-tests, and it's also used by other classes of the current package.
